rigin, but also with additional layers built up in\nthe envelope during infall. Such intriguing links will soon be tested by\nupcoming data from the Rosetta mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Sep 2014 19:19:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-09"}
