gnoring\nthe effects of progenitor bias. A more complete spectroscopic sample is\nrequired at z~2 to properly measure the M/L evolution from the FP evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Sep 2014 20:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
