 from the inefficiency of supersonic\nmotions in the WHIM in triggering solenoidal modes and small-scale twisting of\nmagnetic field structures. Magnetic fields this small will make it hard to\ndetect filaments in radio observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Sep 2014 08:49:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Oct 2014 14:14:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
